  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT348-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">celavuk kuṟippaṟintu vēṟupaṭṭa kiḻattiyait tōḻi vaṟpuṟīiyatu. </p>


        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">The confidante encouraging HER, who changed when she
          understood [his] intention of going. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT348">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> tāmē celpa vāyiṟ kāṉattup</l>
          <l> pulantēr yāṉaik kōṭṭiṭai yoḻinta</l>
          <l> ciṟuvī mullaik kompiṟ ṟāa</l>
          <l> yitaḻaḻin tūṟuṅ kaṇpaṉi matareḻiṟ</l>
          <l> pūṇaka vaṉamulai naṉaittaluṅ</l>
          <l> kāṇār kollō māṇiḻai namarē.</l>


        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>As for him , if he goes ,</l>
          <l rend="indent">doesn't he see, our man with glorious jewellery,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">that also [our] beautiful breasts get wet, inside the ornaments </l>
          <l rend="indent9">of flourishing grace,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">by the dew from the eyes, which oozes destructively </l>
          <l rend="indent9">through petal [lids] ,</l>
          <l rend="indent4">spread like jasmine twigs with little blossoms,</l>
          <l rend="indent4">staying behind between the tusks of an elephant</l>
          <l rend="indent7">searching the fields of the forest?</l>

          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="6b" resp="#Cām">
            <l>doesn't he see, our man, [o you with] glorious jewellery ...</l>
          </lg>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
